[0.000, "o", "\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H; starts up. G,P,C,E & S are abbreviations for the following respective super\r"]
[0.032, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;65r\u001b8\u001b[65d\n\u001b[1;67r\u001b[64;1H; globals: GET, POST, COOKIE, ENV and SERVER. There is a performance penalty\r"]
